@node "com" "Coments of Amitamagotchi"


   Coment in Emulators for the Amiga

AmiTamagotchi

Version: V0.5

Requirements: Any Amiga 

Author: Balrog

 This emulator starts of with just an egg and you watch your new cyber pet
be born. Most functions work like they are supposed to and looks
promising. You are meant to be able to save and load your progress with
the pet, but these functions do not work yet in this version.
This looks the most promising emulator and I look forward to any updates.



   Coment in Amiga Emulators Central

AmiTamagotchi 0.5 beta

Last update: 22/SEP/97

 Feed me, pet me, talk to me! Theres NOTHING to be said
about this! The most decadent toy ever, now on your Amiga! :)

Requirements: 640*480 resolution , 68000 or higher, 1 MB RAM


