@node "What" "What is Amitamagotchi?"


            What is Amitamagotchi?

      AmiTamagotchi is a Tamagotchi (Copyright/TM Bandai) Port to Amiga.
   Tamagotchi is a virtual pet game.

      In this version you can use the "Feed", "Health", "Play",
   "Discipline", "Light", "Duck" and "Medicine" button.

      This program is Postware or Emailware...

      If you use autosave, you must use the "Startup" option.

      This version remember X/Y Cordinates window, and you will can
   conect Amitamagotchi to INTERNET in the next version, with Amirc.

      The light option works now, and a lot of bugs are fixed...

      If this program appears in a magazine, please send me an email.

      This version is the last of Amitamagotchi, read the section
   readme first now!!! for more info.

