@node "How" "How to use"


          How to use

      Use Button A for changing the options(like Food, Health,
   Discipline, Play, ...), and press Button B to select it.

      Use button C for cancel the options.

      You need to wait 5 mins until it is born.

      You can use the options Load and Save.

      With the option Time you see the minutes and hours of life... and
   the type of pet.

      Startup option(See preferences) is for run Amitamagotchi saved
   games if you copy Amitamagotchi in WBstartup drawer.

      If you use the option X/Y, the program remember the cordinates
   if the window.

      If you push Help key, the program execute amitamagotchi.guide

 
      @{B}If you not use MagicWB, run first the program "MWBColors".

